=======================================

Check project homepage for "maybe" up-to-date overview and documentation:
http://glv.sourceforge.net/

Overview:
This program permit to view 3D data easily from the command-line.

View INSTALL text for compilation instructions.

==== Directory structure ==============

src/    : Source files; to build "glv" application
filters/: Input filters; can be used in combination with glv
samples/: Small sample files.  Larger examples can be found on the website
                                                                
